              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "Authors argues for the need of a job recommender system for fresh college graduates. The current system is flawed in the sense that in only considers the one-way student desires, often not taking into account ever-changing differences in student behavior. ",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
