    {
      "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-80be-8d1f-f73fcb419cbf",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Thus, authors propose a recommender that that aggregates learner preferences and needs while also taking into consideration employers. Interestingly, the authors stress the importance of ideological and political education to their recommender framework. ",
